videos.headline: LSU's Edwards-Helaire manuevers his way in for TD
videos.description: LSU RB Clyde Edwards-Helaire takes the hand off and finds his way for a five-yard touchdown run to score on the Tigers' opening drive.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (LSU's Edwards-Helaire manuevers his way in for TD) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow finds Jefferson for a wide-open TD
videos.description: Joe Burrow tosses a 12-yards pass into the end zone to a wide-open Justin Jefferson for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow finds Jefferson for a wide-open TD) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas A&M player appears to fake injury
videos.description: Before Joe Burrow can snap the ball, Texas A&M LB Buddy Johnson falls to the ground, causing play to stop.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas A&M player appears to fake injury) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow finds Chase in stride for 78-yard TD
videos.description: Joe Burrow lobs a pass deep downfield to Ja'Marr Chase, who catches and flies across the goal line to complete a 78-yard touchdown play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow finds Chase in stride for 78-yard TD) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: LSU's Davis-Price muscles in for the TD
videos.description: LSU RB Tyrion Davis-Price receives the handoff and powers his way in for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (LSU's Davis-Price muscles in for the TD) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow sets SEC record for passing yards in a season
videos.description: Joe Burrow connects with Clyde Edwards-Helaire for an 11-yard pass, giving Burrow the most passing yards in a single season for a SEC QB.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow sets SEC record for passing yards in a season) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow ties SEC record for TD passes in a season
videos.description: Joe Burrow passes to Ja'Marr Chase for an 18-yard touchdown, which gives Burrow 44 total TD passes on the season, tying a SEC record.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow ties SEC record for TD passes in a season) 2019/11/30 ESHEET
